Approval: event Approval(address indexed owner, address indexed spender, uint256 value)
ConvertlessDeposited: event ConvertlessDeposited(address indexed user, uint256 syntheticAmount, uint256[] stakingAmounts, uint256[] depositLiquidityAmounts, uint256[] feeLiquidityAmounts)
ConvertlessWithdrawn: event ConvertlessWithdrawn(address indexed user, uint256 syntheticAmount, uint256[] outputAmounts, uint256[] feeAmounts, uint256 outputNativeAmount, uint256 feeNativeAmount)
Deposited: event Deposited(address indexed user, address indexed to, uint256 nativeAmount, uint256 syntheticAmount, uint256 feeAmount)
EmergencyWithdrawn: event EmergencyWithdrawn(address indexed user, uint256 syntheticAmount, uint256[] outputAmounts)
FarmsUpdated: event FarmsUpdated((address beacon, uint256 percent, bytes data)[] farms)
Harvested: event Harvested(address indexed user, uint256 reinvestAmount, uint256 feeAmount, uint256 profitAmount, uint256 paidDebtAmount, uint256 remainingDebtAmount)
OwnershipTransferred: event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
Transfer: event Transfer(address indexed from, address indexed to, uint256 value)
Withdrawn: event Withdrawn(address indexed user, address indexed from, uint256 syntheticAmount, uint256 nativeAmount, uint256 feeAmount)
allowance: function allowance(address owner, address spender) view returns (uint256)
approve: function approve(address spender, uint256 amount) returns (bool)
decreaseAllowance: function decreaseAllowance(address spender, uint256 subtractedValue) returns (bool)
deposit: function deposit(uint256 amount, address to, uint256 minMintAmount) returns (uint256 mintAmount)
depositConvertless: function depositConvertless(uint256[] stakingAmounts, uint256 minMintAmount) returns (uint256 mintAmount)
farms: function farms(uint256 index) view returns ((address beacon, uint256 percent, bytes data))
harvest: function harvest(uint256 minRestakingAmount_) returns (uint256 reinvestAmount, uint256 harvestFeeAmount, uint256 profitAmount, uint256 paidDebtAmount, uint256 remainingDebtAmount, uint256 restakingAmount)
increaseAllowance: function increaseAllowance(address spender, uint256 addedValue) returns (bool)
initialize: function initialize(string name_, string symbol_, address owner_, uint256 profit_, address profitToken_, (address beacon, uint256 percent, bytes data)[] farms_) returns (bool)
name: string:name
publishData: function publishData() view returns ((bool published, address publisher))
transfer: function transfer(address to, uint256 amount) returns (bool)
transferFrom: function transferFrom(address from, address to, uint256 amount) returns (bool)
updateFarms: function updateFarms((address beacon, uint256 percent, bytes data)[] farms_, uint256 minRestakingAmount_) returns (uint256 restakingAmount)
withdraw: function withdraw(uint256 amount, address from, uint256 minNativeAmount) returns (uint256 nativeAmount)
